race.comment: SAVVY BEE (11) doesn't win out of turn but has been right there at the past four outings and this is not an overly strong affair. Will be rock-hard fit for this and gets Rodd on board from a low draw. Rates the testing material. PRIDE OF SAVABELLA (7) boasts a win over this track and trip and gets the services of Wiggins in the irons. Among the leading chances. CHAYSE 'N' LEISA (4) put back-to-back wins together before being thereabouts at the past three outings. Only needs some luck navigating from the sticky draw to be playing a role in the outcome. ARTSPACE (1) gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim and may make his presence felt. PRINCETON AWARD (10) best of the rest while fresh.
